Reports that the suspects, who were apprehended inside a bush in Eastern Limpopo were members of a nearby community. During interrogation, Josephine said she was deceived by the taxi man who promised to buy her a mobile phone if she would give in and give her &#8216;cookie&#8217; I didn t know it would end up like this,he told that if i allow him to sleep with me, he would buy me a Camera phone that uses WhatsApp so that i can chat with my friends. I agreed, but i didn t know he will bring me to the bush. i thought he was taking me to his house when he came to pick me with his taxi at the bust stop. Brother to Josephine who reportedly caught the culprits and reported to the police said he noticed something unusual in the way her sister dressed and decided to find out what she was up to.&nbsp;!